      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LOCO KADE (6) is a consistent runner who is having her first try here. Impressive winner latest at Nowra in Mix in quickest time of the program (29.61). Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Well placed and can measure up. SUMMER ANGEL (3) was below best at her last start when 7th at this track following a win (20.74) at Nowra two back. Expected to feature in the finish. MR. ALEXANDER (2) finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive three back in his speedy 22.49 win at Bulli over 400m. Smart winner three back and looks a key chance on that form. ASTRA BELL (1) can sneak into the finish.",
